or less than a month and already we can see the roof over the production area of the site is well on the way to completion!&nbsp;Follow the work as it happens on our <strong><a href=\"/our-distillery/webcams/\">webcams</a></strong>!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>',7);
