dients to make a very delicious vodka, and using traditional artisan methods with our beautiful copper pot still, we will be producing a spirit of outstanding quality. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<li type = \"disc\"><p> Our vodka will be double distilled, making it even purer and smoother</font>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',0.000000,'','2014-02-14',1,1,13,NULL,'lb',NULL,'in',NULL,'in',NULL,'in',0.000000,0,NULL,'DEFAULT'),(36,1,'The Lakes Gin Gift Pack Coming Soon','lakes-gin-gift-pack-coming-soon','lakes-gin-gift-pack-coming-soon','','<FONT COLOR=\"#00000\">\r\n<li type = \"disc\"><p>The Lakes Gin gift pack is the perfect present for any gin lover\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<li type = \"disc\"><p>Beautifully presented in a magnetic gift box with a 70cl bottle of The Lakes Gin and two branded glasses \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>The only gin to be distilled in Cumbria, The Lakes Gin is a truly unique product.  It will be carefully crafted using classic gin botanicals augmented with those native to Cumbria - including juniper, bilberry, heather and meadowsweet. <p></FONT>',0.000000,'','2014-02-26',1,1,10,NULL,'lb',NULL,'in',NULL,'in',NULL,'in',0.000000,0,NULL,'DEFAULT');
